org.jboss.aop.annotation
Class AnnotationRepository

java.lang.Object
  org.jboss.aop.annotation.AnnotationRepository

public class AnnotationRepository
extends Object

Repository for annotations that is used by the ClassAdvisor to override annotations. Generics have not been added to this class since that causes problems with EJB3 who have a class overriding this one

Version:

Author:
